title: Monster
lyrics:
We make, we break, you call me on the telephone
To tell me what is wrong
Did you forget all other conversations?
And everything you already said
But I don't want to be somebody else

Or this monster you have made me out to be

But I don't really feel like be myself when you keep on draining best from me



You take your jealous observations

And throw them in my face

Did you believe that i would want to stay here

And stick around, be your saving grace?



But I don't want to be somebody else

Or this monster you have made me out to be

But I don't really feel like be myself when you keep on draining best from me



All the best from me

All the best from me

All the best from me

All the best form me



We make, we break, you call me on the telephone

To tell me what is wrong
